snippet.title: How to Learn Python FAST with ChatGPT?
snippet.description:
Intro to Python eBook (free) 👉🏼 https://clickhubspot.com/jdz

In this video, I am sharing 4 tips to learn any coding language FAST with ChatGPT. This video is focused on Python for data science but the tips are relevant to any programming language. How have you been using ChatGPT?  Any cool ideas?

Try ChatGPT here: https://chat.openai.com

My Self-Taught Data Science Journey: https://youtu.be/34r9OwjysDM
How I Would Learn Data Science in 2023: https://youtu.be/ZWgRvW8d_N4
